<p rend="chapter">Yamakappakaraṇa-aṭṭhakathā</p>

<p rend="gatha1">Saṅkhepeneva <pb ed="M" n="0.0287" /><pb ed="P" n="0.0052" /><pb ed="V" n="0.0286" /> devānaṃ, devadevo surālaye;</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Kathāvatthuppakaraṇaṃ, desayitvā raṇañjaho.</p>

<p rend="gatha1">Yamassa visayātīto, nānāyamakamaṇḍitaṃ;</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Abhidhammappakaraṇaṃ, chaṭṭhaṃ chaṭṭhāna desako.</p>

<p rend="gatha1">Yamakaṃ ayamāvatta-nīlāmalatanūruho;</p>

<p rend="gatha2">Yaṃ desayi anuppatto, tassa saṃvaṇṇanākkamo;</p>

<p rend="gathalast">Idāni yasmā tasmāssa, hoti saṃvaṇṇanā ayanti.</p>
